name: MFMailComposeResult
desc: Result codes returned when the mail composition interface is dismissed.

items.name: case saved
items.desc: The email message was saved in the user’s drafts folder.

items.name: case sent
items.desc: The email message was queued in the user’s outbox.

items.name: case failed
items.desc: The email message was not saved or queued, possibly due to an error.
